**  ER  (ERROR MESSAGE )
E-01 SCAN DATE FROM ISN'T RIGHT
E-02 SCAN DATE TO ISN'T RIGHT
E-03 DATE TIME ERROR  FROM > TO
E-04 THERE ISN'T SCAN DATA.
E-06 THE FIRST DATA.
E-07 THE LAST DATA.
